snippet.title: REACTION! London Fields Trailer #1 - Amber Heard Movie 2018
snippet.description:
Here's my reaction to the trailer for London Fields! Not too sure what to make of this one other than Amber Heard looking mighty fine! It’s a maybe for me on this one!

What about you? Are you excited for this? What was your favorite part of the trailer? Let me know in the comments!

London Fields Trailer: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cZ2KJtiNZ0U

Clairvoyant femme fatale Nicola Six has been living with a dark premonition of her impending death by murder. She begins a tangled love affair with three uniquely different men: one of whom she knows will be her murderer. 

Starring Amber Heard, Cara Delevingne and Gemma Chan!
